title: Why Amy’s Son Requested a ‘Quiet Dinner’ + Who Wants to Be A Hundredaire + Daphne Oz on The Easiest Recipes Anyone Can Do and Saving Money at Grocery Store
itunes:title: Why Amy’s Son Requested a ‘Quiet Dinner’ + Who Wants to Be A Hundredaire + Daphne Oz on The Easiest Recipes Anyone Can Do and Saving Money at Grocery Store
description:
Amy talks about why her son last night requested they don't talk while having dinner last night. Holly plays a round of Who Wants To Be A Hundredaire to win $100 bucks! Can Morgan take home the Elder vs. Millennial championship today? We’ll find out! We talk to Daphne Oz about her TV show “The Good Dish”, easiest recipes anyone can make and how families can save money at the grocery store.
